Troubleshooting Tips
Zeek not capturing traffic:

Verify correct network interface in node.cfg
Check permissions: sudo /opt/zeek/bin/zeekctl status
Ensure interface is up: ip link show
NetFlow data not collecting:

Verify nfcapd is running: ps aux | grep nfcapd
Check softflowd status: ps aux | grep softflowd
Ensure port 9995 is not blocked: sudo netstat -tulpn | grep 9995
Python script errors:

Install required packages: pip3 install pandas numpy
Check file paths in script configuration
Verify NetFlow data exists: ls -la /var/log/netflow/
No anomalies detected:

Ensure baseline is established first
Generate more diverse traffic patterns
Adjust anomaly_threshold value (lower = more sensitive)
